  * Update parted from 3.4->3.5
  * Update nspr-4.32 -> nspr-4.34
  * Update liberation-fonts from 2.1.4 -> 2.1.5
  * Fix glibc after changes with 3.24
  * Update mtools version 4.0.35 -> 4.0.40
