  * Update elfutils to 0.187
  * Update to gzip 1.12
  * Update GnuTLS to 3.7.6
  * Update automake to 1.16.5
  * aspell: Patch for CVE-2019-25051

freedesktop-sdk-22.08beta.1:

  * Several buildstream plugins have been upstreamed: cpan, pypi, patch_queue, snap_image
    check_forbidden
  * Update all the components to the latest version available, check specific versions at
    https://gitlab.com/freedesktop-sdk/freedesktop-sdk/-/wikis/Release-Contents#contents
  * A lot of other small fixes and improvements

