freedesktop-sdk-20.08beta.1:

    * pango: Build with libthai support
    * Move flex to SDK only. Leave only libfl in Platform.
    * Move gobject introspection gir files to SDK only
    * python: Swap usercustomize and sitecustomize
    * gcc: Enable Objective C and Objective C++
    * harfbuzz: Disable HB_LANGUAGE_INVALID in introspection
    * dictionaries: Fix missing/broken Catalan and Norwegian dictionaries
    * ffmpeg: Add MPEG-2, Intel Indeo, VP6, MS-MPEG DivX;), ape
    * dwz: Move to to SDK
    * Remove systemd.pc from SDK
    * Add openjpeg
    * Add cython
    * Add lz4
    * Add SPIRV tools and glslang to SDK
    * python3-pip: Move to SDK only
    * gobject-introspection: Add documentation tool
    * itstool: Fix typo in element name
    * grep: Enable perl regexp
    * Remove mesa-aco extension now mesa extension supports it.
    * python: Add /usr/bin/python symlink to python3
    * glibc: Fix $LIB (#874)
    * Add libjack drop-in replacement from pipewire
    * Add cython, python3-pygments, python3-wheel
    * Add libportal
    * Add brotli
    * Add lz4
    * Add openjpeg
    * Add wget
    * Add opusfile
    * Removed libcroco
    * Removed cups
    * Removed dconf
    * linux-headers: Update to 5.7.3
    * glibc: Update to 2.31
    * ncurses: Update to 6.2
    * binutils: Update to 2.34
    * coreutils: Update to 8.32
