    * Add Docker and OCI images
    * curl: updaet to 7.65.1
    * nss: update to 3.44
    * nspr: update to 4.1
    * glibc: Fix proble with LD_AUDIT
    * rust: update to 1.35
    * glibc: update to 2.29
    * gawk: Update to 5.0.0
    * gnupg: Update to 2.2.16
    * libgpg-error: Update to 1.36
    * Fix setuids (VM)
    * Add pwquality (VM)
    * Remove intltool
    * ostree: Enable GObject introspection (VM)
    * freedesktop-sdk/freedesktop-sdk!1391: Update to 2.27
    * sqlite: Update to 3.28
    * Mesa: disable xa state tracker
    * Add /etc/shells (VM)
    * glib: Update to 2.60.3
    * glib-networking: Update to 2.60.2
    * openssl: Update to 1.1.1c
    * libfdk-aac: update to fedora snapshot
    * ffmpeg: Update to n4.1.3
    * gstreamer*: Bump to 1.16.0
    * binutils: update to 2.32
    * gstreamer-vaapi: disable gallium driver
    * Remove shared-library-guard (#723)
    * Fix Vulkan and OpenCL ICD detection (#785)
    * setuptools: update to 41.0.1
    * pip: update to 19.1.1
    * opus: update to 1.3.1
    * Add pipewire (#446)
    * glib: Build documentation (#779)
    * Add 32bit Intel VAAPI extension (#438)
    * Add echo cancellation support (#633)
    * Add libnice (#634)
    * Add xserver with xwayland to the VM
    * Add cross compilers (#348)
    * Provide multiarch SDK to enable cross compilation
    * buildsystem-autotools: add which and remove redundant which and gettext
      dependencies (#765)
    * PAM fixes for the VM
    * Drop linux-pam from flatpak runtime
    * gcc: update to 9.1
    * Support using valgrind without Debug extension installed (#751)
    * Fixes to make flatpak-pip-generator work (#575)
    * Fixed gtk-doc symlinks in .Doc extension (#738)
    * Make mesa drivers an extension (#697)
    * Rename html5-codecs extension to ffmpeg-html5
    * LLVM: update to 8.0
    * cargo: use bundled version from rust
